    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Let us wor--ship the Word,___ O ye faith-ful,__ prais--ing___ Him__ that with the Fa---ther__ and Spir---it is co-be--gin--ning--less___ God,__ Who was born of___ a__ pure__ Vir-gin____ that__ we all__ be___ saved;__ for____ He was pleased to___ mount__ the__ Cross____ in the flesh that___ He__ as--sumed, ac-cept-ing thus___ to__ en-dure___ death. And by His glo-ri--ous ris---ing, He al-so willed to res-ur-rect____ the___ dead."
    }
